AULA 1

Istalar node.js (chocolatey) = https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/#windows

instalar VSCode = https://code.visualstudio.com/

npm install nodemon -D
//-D = Desenvolvimento

//remover essa linha do package.json
"test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1"
//E substituir por:
"start": "nodemon index.js"
//escrever npm start no TERMINAL

